{"tid":2082021,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來台灣一早有本土書寫系統(白話字)","createTime":"2020-06-27T16:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T04:29:39.000Z","uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfbe7326cf0cc6e2b420bb7e6b6b4b31a4f6f466","tid":2082021,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"白話字(Pe̍h-ōe-jī, 又稱教羅)係19世紀初被傳教士創造出黎既羅馬書寫系統, 用黎寫聖經。曾經, 有台灣既報紙同文學係用白話字創作, 實現我手寫我口。直至國民黨蔣匪打壓, 台灣既本土文字先被外來既漢字取代。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3LKY6LDS8z8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3LKY6LDS8z8&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=61b6e126\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3LKY6LDS8z8</a><br />\n<br />\n台語同我地一樣係南方語系, 同音字無北佬話咁嚴重, 我地廢除漢字改用拼音問題細好多。用漢字根本表達唔到我地詞彙豐富既母語, 例如有俚語係無字可用, 只要轉哂用拼音就無問題。如果台灣人可以用拼音文字寫一本母語聖經, 咁點解香港人唔可以用羅馬字母書寫粵語? <br />\n<br />\n已經有台灣人做緊母語字復興(例如<a href=\"https://twitter.com/saipakhootw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsaipakhootw&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=299827c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/saipakhootw</a>),  只有廢除漢字, 我地先可以保護本土文化, 同中國畜牲一刀兩斷, 實現文化隔離。"},{"pid":"589080b6d80d08306da803ab6559a6d433339bbd","tid":2082021,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"台語，同閩南話，有咩分別？"},{"pid":"fc3f517489ed036c2f31bcb9fe4864c95221b63e","tid":2082021,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"589080b6d80d08306da803ab6559a6d433339bbd","tid":2082021,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"台語，同閩南話，有咩分別？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"你當閩南話係西班牙文<br />\n台語係南美嘅西班牙文"},{"pid":"065b29e803cc5e7c068ca7d7fa488d5b713686ea","tid":2082021,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"我注定要學中文，但我希望我嘅子孫唔使學"},{"pid":"8c